<section xmlns="http://xml.house.gov/schemas/uslm/1.0" style="-uslm-lc:I80" id="id050f6915-3a70-11f1-8ace-823fb135378d" identifier="/us/usc/t19/s81q"><num value="81q">§ 81q.</num><heading> Transfer of grant</heading><content>
<p style="-uslm-lc:I11" class="indent0">The grant shall not be sold, conveyed, transferred, set over, or assigned.</p>
</content><sourceCredit id="id050f6916-3a70-11f1-8ace-823fb135378d">(<ref href="/us/act/1934-06-18/ch590/s17">June 18, 1934, ch. 590, § 17</ref>, <ref href="/us/stat/48/1002">48 Stat. 1002</ref>.)</sourceCredit>
</section>
